  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fingerspelling Unleashed – BANZSL Edition</h2>Fingerspelling itself is using hand movements to spell out words that do not have an established sign. It is commonly used to spell out the names of people or places. <br><br><br>This Edition of the game focuses on teaching you BANZSL, which is short for British Sign Language (BSL), Australian Sign Language (AUSLAN) & New Zealand Sign Language (NZSL). All three languages use the same two handed sign language fingerspelling alphabet.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Low system requirements.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>User Friendly Interface.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Relaxing piano melodies.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A game saving system.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fun Mini Games (see below)</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Type To Defend</h2> Typing game with a twist!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283800/extras/0ca2d846f24eb700c8a27da7548c1845.poster.avif?t=1702355294\" width=526 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283800/extras/0ca2d846f24eb700c8a27da7548c1845.webm?t=1702355294\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283800/extras/0ca2d846f24eb700c8a27da7548c1845.mp4?t=1702355294\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Identify and Type</h2> Can you identify the word?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283800/extras/8729203f83a852d450af10b0cd0abd18.poster.avif?t=1702355294\" width=526 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283800/extras/8729203f83a852d450af10b0cd0abd18.webm?t=1702355294\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Word Search</h2> Like Word Searches? Find them too easy? Then try this!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283800/extras/db11b91ac599d95c09c28d0dbe719aa4.webp?t=1702355294\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283800/extras/db11b91ac599d95c09c28d0dbe719aa4.poster.avif?t=1702355294\" class=\"bb_img\" width=526 height=280 /></picture></span>",
